{
  "stem": "9728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were smart enough not to give us any greasy food or any fat, you know, because this is a-- you know, after-- after so many years of not eating right, it was terrible, you know.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I made friends with the-- with some of those at the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My health was not the best health.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was missing several teeth, because some teeth were knocked out by a-- by a a German with a-- with a spade during-- during work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't perform the work, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- so he took his spade handle, and he-- he shellacked me under my chin, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he knocked out a couple teeth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in that Camp Number Three.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was in Camp Number Three.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beaten-- now, at that terrible beating, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But a kick and a-- and a slam [INAUDIBLE] thing, this was on a daily-- this was on a daily order.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But coming back to the thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In that camp, we were given also a care package-- the first care package, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we ate our full.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, I don't want to say that I didn't have to go 10 or 15 times to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Probably so it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eh, I didn't feel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The nerves-- my nerves were gone already from-- from all the years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But see, bodily, well, I could survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could survive bodily.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stayed in that camp in the Bad Toelz about three, four days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, as I said, the camp was so, so luxury that the Germans-- that the Americans decided that they are going to take it for their soldiers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which, I don't blame them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can-- I can see.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
